extends ./layouts/layout

block content
  // MAIN CONTENT
  .container
    //.hero-unit
    //  h2 Welcome to Structure-Guided Drug Design System 
    .hero-unit
      h2 How to use FragRep ?
    .hero-unit
      h2
      h3  1. On the xundrug.cn/fragrep website, please choose a protein and a ligand file and then click the upload button. 
      p
      br     
      h2
         img(src='/pkcsm/static/img/FragRep_input.png', style='border: none;', width='700')

    .hero-unit
      h3  2. The server presents all replaceable substructures on the input ligand. Please select the substructure you want to modify and click the 'Submit' button and wait for two minitues.
      p    
      br
      h2
         img(src='/pkcsm/static/img/mol3dopt_2.png', style='border: none;', width='1000')
    .hero-unit
      h3  3. The system finds suitable fragments that fit well with local protein environment and assemble new molecules. The result page shows information on newly generated analogues.
      p 
      br
      h2
         img(src='/pkcsm/static/img/mol3dopt_3.png', style='border: none;', width='1000')



    .hero-unit
      h3 Contact
      h2     
      p If you have any question about FragRep, please contact:
      p Changge Ji 
      p Chicago.ji@gmail.com



